        "subject": "LU-11549 tests: link succeded to an ophan remote object",
        "message": "LU-11549 tests: link succeded to an ophan remote object\n\nAn open file gets unlinked by rename,\nat the same time a cross-mdt link is able to create a name\nfor a dying object. Also e2fsck sees an unconnected inode\nafter the file gets closed .\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly=true mdtcount=2 envdefinitions=ONLY=104 testlist=sanityn\nCray-bug-id: LUS-6208\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Zarochentsev <c17826@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I10056638c1c16fad70ef549efa7b762291dab24e\n"
